Im back... i know its been a while but i am now writing again. School starts on the 9th so its back to the classroom. *sigh* i dislike school so very much but at least ill be able to see some of my friends.  Right now im watching my friends pets while she is in orlando with her family. everything is just peachy at least i get cash! :0 *did i say that out loud? grins* yeah i admit it im a broke girl who needs money for my books and everything else cuz my parents are cheap. my kittys are still the cutest things on the planet! they have grown to almost double what they were when we first got them but whose complaining? *certainly not me* we just got back from visiting my family up in jacksonville my sister had a dr.s appointment there so we just visited the relatives up there. we had a good time. we got some shrimp and me and my mom visited my cuz nancy lee and she doing a hell of a lot better than what she was she had a staff infection in her lower back and she got really sick and she has been sick for two years. so im glad shes doing better. my little cuz michelle has grown soo much. she starts kindergarden this year and i swear it was just yesturday that she was just born and i was holding her she was so tiny. and she kept wanting me to do that superman thing (you know were your dad or someone else held your hands and lifted you into the air with their feet?) well i started that and now i regret that sooo much. yeah i was busy this week. and to give yall a break cuz i dont know what else to write ill leave you all alone to read on other peoples journals.  have a good day or night were ever you are.
